  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Socio-professional data collection, medical, psychological, demographic, economic, and
      educational to patients within the care pathway  for cancer of the upper aero-digestive
      tract.

      A series of questionnaires will be presented at the initial consultation and then 6 months,
      12 months and 18 months during follow-up visits. Medical data will be collected via the CRF.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
